 nation\", \"from\": 2393, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"economic competitiveness\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Money alone is not enough.\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2476, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Money\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There must be grit to win.\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"grit\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's population of 1.4 billion people is about four times that of the US.\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2504, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999771900666369, \"rank\": 1.8582966444660962e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 2577, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9321447910116158, \"rank\": 0.07111238883156804, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1.4 billion people\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2544}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Comparatively, then the US is more competitive than China.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2606, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9321447910116158, \"rank\": 0.07111238883156804, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2634, \"end\": 2639, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999771900666369, \"rank\": 1.8582966444660962e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://