war\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2912}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many countries misunderstand the US, complaining about its arrogance, riches, dominance, imposition of its will, a big army terrorizing other nations and supplying weapons, for example to Israel and Taiwan.\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2959, \"end\": 2961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9321447910116158, \"rank\": 0.07111238883156804, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3114, \"end\": 3120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"score\": 0.9999999653878154, \"rank\": 3.45848253003114e-08, \"text\": \"Israel\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel\"}, {\"begin\": 3125, \"end\": 3131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9998368212642214, \"rank\": 0.00016271606845881282, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many countries\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"its arrogance\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"riches\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"dominance\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3013}, {\"ngram\": \"imposition\", \"from\": 3015, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"a big army\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"other nations\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3075}, {\"ngram\": \"weapons\", \"from\": 3090, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"example\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only language the Americans understand is competitive behaviour as China has learnt and also demonstrated.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3205, \"end\": 3210, \"title\": \"ht